headline: Shah's Halal Food Becomes Official Partner of MetLife Stadium, Bringing Authentic Halal Cuisine to Giants and Jets Fans
summary: Shah's Halal Food today announced a new partnership with MetLife Stadium, home of the New York Jets and New York Football Giants, to bring NYC's authentic Halal cuisine to the venue's dining options. The collaboration features three strategically located food service areas throughout the stadium, enhancing the culinary experience for the diverse fanbase that calls MetLife Stadium home.
